    <date day="25" month="July" year="2023"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>   The authoritative version of RFCs are published in an XML format.
   This format is chosen for its ability to capture semantic details.  A
   high-level process is described for the revision of the RFC XML
   format.

	 </t>
